      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable daily driver for someone who doesn't mind a bit of character. The exterior shows its age with some clear coat peeling on the roof and a few minor door dings from city parking. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows visible wear on the driver's seat and some staining on the floor mats. Mechanically, the car runs and drives well, though it will soon be due for a brake pad replacement and has a slow seep from the valve cover gasket. It is a solid, functional vehicle that would benefit from some cosmetic TLC and routine maintenance.",
