      "description": "Hey there! I'm looking to find a new home for my trusty car. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been such a reliable companion for me! It drives beautifully and has been well-loved and looked after. Whether you need a dependable daily driver or something for your next road trip, this one is ready to go. Come check it out\u2014I\u2019m sure you\u2019ll love it as much as I have!",
