    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist\u2019s specification, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system. The power is delivered through a tactile Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M differential lock, ensuring exceptional power delivery through the corners. To address common platform weaknesses, the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced, and the rod bearings have been serviced for peace of mind. The chassis remains taut, utilizing its original MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension geometry for precise handling. While the exterior shows the honest patina of an enjoyed driver\u2019s car, the mechanical vitals are synchronized and ready for the redline. This is a robust, mechanically sound example of BMW\u2019s finest naturally aspirated era.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
