    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This well-maintained vehicle presents beautifully in its original factory finish, retaining a deep luster that reflects its life spent mostly in a climate-controlled garage. The exterior shows only the minor, expected signs of careful road use, such as light stone chipping on the front fascia. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary of comfort; the leather upholstery has been regularly conditioned and shows only slight softening on the driver\u2019s side bolster, while the dashboard and trim are free of sun damage or cracks. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health, having followed a strict preventative maintenance schedule with all fluids recently serviced. It starts eagerly, idles smoothly, and the transmission provides crisp, confident shifts. Every electronic feature, from the dual-zone climate control to the premium audio system, functions exactly as intended. Sold with a complete set of owner\u2019s manuals and a comprehensive folder of service receipts, this car represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a reliable, turn-key experience.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
