    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and she\u2019s been absolute gold to me. It\u2019s in really solid shape, super reliable, and honestly a joy to drive! I\u2019ve made sure to keep up with the maintenance so it\u2019s totally ready for its next adventure with you. If you\u2019re looking for a dependable car that still looks great on the road, you\u2019ve found it. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to see this go to a great home!",
      "price": 32500.0,
