    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sorted E46 M3 featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six, boasting individual throttle bodies and a high-revving 8,000 RPM redline. This example features a crisp 6-speed manual transmission and the critical rear subframe reinforcement already performed. The VANOS unit has been overhauled for precise variable valve timing, and a recent valve clearance adjustment ensures optimal valvetrain harmonics. The chassis is tightened with upgraded bushings and Koni dampers, maintaining excellent lateral stability and communicative steering feedback. While the aesthetic reflects honest use, the powertrain exhibits robust compression and a linear power band. Recent preventative maintenance includes a cooling system refresh and a high-quality 10W-60 synthetic oil service.",
